4:28:25.000Z","msg":"首先 認清楚目標係咩<br />\n呢句聽落好on9，但好重要，因為做既野會好唔同。<br />\n<br />\n目標分好多種，不過主要係：<br />\n1 beat the market <br />\n意思係回報高過恆指，呢個係所有active inventors既目標，好撚難。<br />\n<br />\n2 要市場回報<br />\n即係買指數基金。 你見好多巴絲成日講話2800盈富基金就係追恆指 ，而恆指就係港股指標(如果咁撚多支那股入左成份股你都仍然覺得佢代表到香港既話)，所以2800係市場回報。<br />\n<br />\n有目標之後，就講方法。<br />\n<br />\n買個別股票既，有基本分析既，有睇技術圖表既，有求神問卜既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，主要睇你buy邊套。<br />\n<br />\n買指數基金既，可以一手手咁睇啱買，亦可以月供，睇需要決定。 <br />\n<br />\n打住咁多先<br />\n<br />\n(其實可能巴打已經知道，係我係度9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"acb4a686c5d3f579535e73e5ed8822692e8245de","tid":1701344,"uid":47758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b73a0915e48766332c5b901968049a830945453","tid":1701344,"uid":74385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df44c5afcb3acc2c0555a33645b4ca65c0d4ae6","tid":1701344,"uid":47758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7be7680bf796da44c6e20a3680f8757a0f21144e","tid":1701344,"uid":74385,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:13:31.000Z","msg":"係咩 platform好用？ 有無啲名可以 google下？ 唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:15:40.000Z","msg":"ib 都有paper account 玩啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:16:14.000Z","msg":"要開 acct入幾皮落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"我開嗰陣入左一皮港紙咋喎，好似係寄支票先要入八萬"},{"pid":"771f79b47c14d72193f7f8e5af8df896f7a39c49","tid":1701344,"uid":324892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:31:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d65e13ce386fd5921d6e19f8f8f646a54c20d98","tid":1701344,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:19:26.000Z","msg":"@ES @YM @NQ @CL @S @W @C"},{"pid":"28fc137c7665909324d075ed20a67ced999d3681","tid":1701344,"uid":314121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p